{"type": "article", "id": 55553, "title": "Nike 集团将为 10% 员工加薪，以及，Balenciaga 入驻京东旗下奢侈电商 Toplife | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-07-24T10:48:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1066, "name": "Calvin Klein"}, {"id": 4949, "name": "Guess"}, {"id": 52099, "name": "KIKO"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 52100, "name": "NIKE"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180724184327eEWflQx5Hw0AMVGa.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Superdry-founder-Dunkerton-sells-6-7-percent-stake,1000562.html#.W1by-NgzZp8\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Superdry 创始人&nbsp;</strong><strong>Julian Dunkerton&nbsp;</strong><strong>抛售 公司 6.7% 股份</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong>| 抛售后，Julian Dunkerton 手中的股份降至 18.5%。他以每股 1285 便士的价格一共卖出 550 万股、套现 7100 万英镑。周一（7 月 23 日）闭市时，Superdry 的股价为每股 1365 便士，市值为 11.2 亿英镑。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Nike-to-raise-wages-for-thousands-of-employees,1000417.html#.W1bzCNgzZp8\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike 集团宣布将为 7500 名员工加薪</a></strong> | 这项决定是在 Nike 集团内部职场行为调查结束 2 个月后作出的。这项调查导致数名高管离职，并引来诸多抱怨。此次加薪将于 8 月开始，覆盖 Nike 集团全球 10% 的员工。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://tech.ifeng.com/a/20180724/45079332_0.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\">意大利平价化妆品牌 KIKO 入驻天猫</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 意大利美妆品牌 Kiko Milano、Deborah集团、Diego dalla Palma 以及 RVB Lab 于上周五正式入驻天猫国际。双方在“Tmall Discovery”首届欧洲峰会上共同宣布了这一合作关系，命名为“The Colors of Italian Beauty”。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/financial/balenciaga-joins-jd-com-toplife-china-1202763544/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Balenciaga 入驻京东旗下奢侈电商平台 Toplife</a></strong> | 此前开云集团旗下加入该平台的品牌还有 Alexander McQueen 和 Saint Laurent。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/media/vanity-fair-radhika-jones-layoffs-sunhee-grinnell-1202763400/\" rel=\"nofollow\">《名利场》美妆主编&nbsp;SunHee Grinnell 离职</a></strong>&nbsp;| SunHee Grinnell 于 1991 年加入《名利场》，2008 年起担任美妆总监。新任主编 Radhika Jones 上任后，《名利场》开始大幅削减成本，资深员工亦纷纷离职。此前离职的还包括在职 12 年的创意总监&nbsp;Jessica Diehl、在职 7 年的时尚总监&nbsp;Michael Carl 等。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://fashionista.com/2018/07/calvin-klein-fall-2018-ad-campaign\" rel=\"nofollow\">Calvin Klein 发布 2018 秋冬大片</a></strong>。</p><p>本系列大片由 Willy Vanderperre 掌镜，在犹他州拍摄。模特看上去都比背景里的山丘岩石大得多，试图制造一种怀旧而奇异的氛围。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180724183243IHcbVtP6lS1gwCJG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.714500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180724183258LPRpA9IxUvWJO8T7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.714500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180724183308IvwMENj1Y84CP3tB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.714500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807241833180YNzsqLA73DHbc6d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.714500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807241833295YSOGlTcQmRWAuXL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.714500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180724183340E2mOYNI81rtDQxdw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.714500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807241833519fA3SR4OvWpcVJw7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.714500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807241834043FsylwZT9Jo40dVI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.714500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180724183416AQ8XUJBFKr3EIPLC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.714500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180724183430TAcvtsOQZ7m385Hg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.714500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180724183440ztXLSxZwsJWm6pkc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.714500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Guess-unveils-nostalgic-desert-road-trip-campaign-for-Fall-2018,1000404.html#.W1by-NgzZp8\" rel=\"nofollow\">Guess 发布 2018 秋冬大片，由&nbsp;Josh Ryan 在加州的约书亚树国家公园（Joshua Tree）拍摄</a></strong>。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807241816458M9XSJtB2DA5adbn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180724181653gMfklZB02c8tEb1j.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180724181633BSx7IDjgEocZ2U1A.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.566667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018072418170889T3FCYLh46gQONz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.267500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180724181717Hcjya0endo3LhiJM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499574\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180724181726srBOMHq0ubtDA3zG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.318333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/342201/puma-yuyishujia-shantell-martin-dailai-2018-qiudongxilie/\" rel=\"nofollow\">PUMA 与英国视觉艺术家 Shantell Martin 再次推出联名系列</a></strong>。<br></p><p>本系列中包含四款鞋、防风外套以及两用背包，已于 7 月 21 日通过<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cn.puma.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> PUMA 官网</a>、门店以及各指定零售商发售。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180724181346QGoFW0XxStCehUNP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180724181406B4AN8TJqgGjLas6c.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807241814190PYBCeva1jWtEFKD.j